videos.description: Wichita State transfer Austin Reaves picks the ball away from Texas and takes it the other way for a monster slam early in the first.

videos.description: Texas' Royce Hamm Jr. shows his strength with a powerful block on Oklahoma's Alondes Williams in the first half.
